"If Magmatron wants her dead than he will have to go through us first." Gravedigger said to himsle. Shredder had left with a fem bot so they had to get blondertron to a cr chamber quickly. "Copper go into copter mode and fly around until you find the cr chamber. Put her in your cockpit."

    Copper flew with great speed around the base. He found a cr tank and quickly dropped her in it. She'll be better in no time.
